msgctxt "68_Chigusa"
msgid "So the package here will tell me how you really feel about\\r\n"\n"me? What's that supposed to mean?"
msgstr "¿Así que el paquete que hay aquí me dirá lo que\\r\n"\n"realmente sientes por mí? ¿Qué quiere decir?"

msgctxt "80_Kiryu"
msgid "I couldn't say. I guess you'll find out once you hand that\\r\n"\n"slip to the man behind the counter."
msgstr "Ni idea. Supongo que lo descubrirás cuando le des ese\\r \n"\n"recibo al hombre detrás del mostrador."

msgctxt "92_Chigusa"
msgid "...Right. Let's go inside."
msgstr "...Ya. Entremos."

